1797506b-5ef3-5522-a5a1-989df8791443,tg:rubgr:1806,e73_Descriptions,,id.desc,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,"

Good Shepherd (Kronacker). The wolf to be compared with Jan Bruegel's fox in 'Allegory of Earth' (Terrestrial Paradise), Louvre (detail) repr. in colour in M. Eemans, Brueghel de Velours, Brussels 1964, pl. XI, p. 94 and complete in black & white, pl. 16. The complete picture also repr. in Gerbrande WINKELMANN-Rhein, Blumen-Brueghel, Cologne 1968 black & white plate 21. For Good and unfaithful shepherd also the painting attributed to C. Massys (before the war with T. Harris), see Witt Library, to be taken into account.
